Given an array of integers nums, sort the array in ascending order and return it using heap sort.

Example 1:
Input: nums = [5,2,3,1]
Output: [1,2,3,5]

Example 2:
Input: nums = [5,1,1,2,0,0]
Output: [0,0,1,1,2,5]

Link to Problem: https://leetcode.com/problems/sort-an-array/description/
Provide a screenshot of the accepted solution on Leetcode, including the left pane in the description of pull request and push the solution.
